reviewText: love the dvd, great price and fast delivery
Fast shipping, great seller, and great dvd my daughter loves her timmy dvd.

My daughter loves Timmy so we bought the dvd for our 1/2 a country move road trip and it was a god send.  I will have to order more since Disney jr changed the time he plays and its too early for her to see.
My toddler loves Timmy Time and Shaun the sheep. This show is even enjoyable for adults and older kids. No dialogue, which is a nice change from other shows.

Timmy Time is the preschool version of Shaun the Sheep and it is a cute show that I don't mind watching with my boys!  There are fun songs and typical preschool behavior that my boys can relate to.  The animals are all adorable and it is a claymation-type show which is a nice break from cartoons.

My son loves Timmy. He watches it in the car. The theme song is very catchy and none of the characters actually talk. They just make the noises of whatever animal they are. I feel like this sets up reasonable expectations for when he sees real life sheep.

I gave it 3stars only because it entertained my grandson. I think it didn't have enough language content for any age! For children at the age this is suited for it should have much more language. Good silly content but that's about all.
We love Timmy Time DVDs! Even there's no words, it's easy to understand the message & it's so cute! My 2 years old daughter loves all these DVDs & so is my 6 year old one :)
We enjoy Shawn the Sheep- and now Timmy!  Our toddler can't get enough of this video!
It's Timmy Time on a DVD... How can you go wrong with that?
Arrived quickly and exactly as described.  This was a huge hit with my 2 year old, he laughs a ton when watching.
good price shipped very fast thanks
